**Summary:**
This documentation explains Amplitude's Engagement Matrix chart feature for analyzing product engagement patterns by plotting events in a four-quadrant matrix based on breadth (% of active users) and frequency (average executions per day/period), helping identify high/low performing features for optimization or deprecation decisions.

